These are Puzzles for 6x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, soy-milk, coffee, mirinda
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, coach, freelancer, security-guard
City: berlin, venice, edinburgh, san-francisco
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, daisy, daffodil, marigold
4 different pets are kept: bird, chinchilla, lizard, rabbit
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, skateboarding, cycling, soccer
 1. the owner of the rabbit is the person who growsdaffodil##1
 2. the analyst is the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
 3. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
 4. the person who's sport is cycling is on the far right##1
 5. the person traveling to edinburgh is the owner of the chinchilla##1
 6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person traveling to venice is on the left or right of the person traveling to edinburgh##3
 8. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the freelancer is the person drinking mirinda##1
10. the person who's sport is cricket is the person traveling to venice##1
11. the person who growsmarigold is on the left or right of the person traveling to venice##3
12. the security-guard is the person drinking soy-milk##1
13. the analyst is in an even position##4
14. the security-guard is the person who growsdaisy##1
15. the person traveling to berlin is the person drinking soy-milk##1
16. the analyst is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
17. the coach is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |       4        |
| Beverage         | mirinda    | hot-chocolate      | coffee | soy-milk        |
| Job           | freelancer | analyst     | coach     | security-guard |
| City   | venice   | edinburgh | san-francisco   | berlin         |
| Flower   | bellflower  | marigold        | daffodil   | daisy            |
| Pet           | bird       | chinchilla  | rabbit    | lizard         |
| Sport     | cricket       | skateboarding     | soccer     | cycling      |

