.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-4-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, juice, lemonade, soy-milk
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, prince, chaman, game
There are 4 different favourite colors: blue, blood-red, coral, aquamarine
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, pomegranate, kale, cauliflower
4 different pets are kept: frog, guinea-pig, lizard, mouse
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, swimming, weightlifting, rowing
 1. the person who likes blue is on the left or right of the person eating kale##3
 2. the person drinking soy-milk is in an even position##4
 3. the person eating kale is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
 4. the ritmeester-smoker is the person eating cauliflower##1
 5. the ritmeester-smoker is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 6. the person eating pomegranate is the prince-smoker##1
 7. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
 8. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the owner of the frog##3
 9. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
10. the prince-smoker is the person who likes aquamarine##1
11. the person drinking lemonade is in an odd position##4
12. the person who likes blue is the person who's sport is rowing##1
13. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far left or far right##3
14. the owner of the mouse is the person who likes aquamarine##1
15. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
16. the game-smoker is on the right of the person who likes coral##1
17. the person eating kale is on the left or right of the game-smoker##3
18. the person eating kale is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |      4      |
