 1. the security-guard is the person who likes pink##1
 2. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the security-guard##1
 3. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the person who likes pink##3
 4. the person traveling to prague is on the far right##1
 5. the person who likes coral is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 6. the librarian is the person traveling to rome##1
 7. the owner of the turtle is between the owner of the lizard and the person who likes light-blue##2
 8. the person playing go is the owner of the snake##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in may is between the person traveling to berlin and the freelancer##2
10. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
11. the person traveling to rome is on the far left##1
12. the person playing snooker is in an odd position##4
13. the owner of the lizard is on the far left or far right##3
14. the person playing chess is on the right of the person playing snooker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2        |     3      |     4      |
